# Media storage policy

Follow the canonical policy in [`docs/media-policy.md`](../../docs/media-policy.md)
(also summarized in [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md)).

In short: commit images/sound **under 2 MB** under `exhibits/<slug>/media/`; send
video and files **≥ 2 MB** to the external media store; never commit secrets or
media-heavy Xibo export ZIPs. Full rules: `docs/media-policy.md`.
